{"tid":851730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港未來10年投資超過1萬億基建　張建宗：要投資未來","createTime":"2018-10-07T11:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T13:35:19.000Z","uid":117200,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e9799009a9777dc4b9a585e6225716317e4ae10e","tid":851730,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170904/_2017090418555591830.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170904%2F_2017090418555591830.jpg&h=47bc6907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗今早(7日)發表網誌表示，政府投資基建項目，有時被批評為「大白象」工程，浪費公帑，但今天回首一看，事實勝於雄辯。他又指「投資基建等於投資未來」，預計未來5年，香港每年的整體建造工程量會維持在2500億港元至3000億港元的高水平，未來十年政府在基建總投資將超過1萬億港元。<br />\n<br />\n他舉例指，上世紀70年代地下鐵路建造時，同樣受到部分人質疑其必要性及鐵路的安全性，惟時至今日，香港擁有現代化高效的鐵路系統，每日超過530萬人次乘搭港鐵，並反問「假如今天香港沒有地下鐵路，我們的生活會如何」。"},{"pid":"a0bd06db8d97be5d2290e49a0261bc77477fc128","tid":851730,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:20:03.000Z","msg":"他亦指赤鱲角香港國際機場啟用20年來，大大推動香港空運發展，航空貨運量連續8年位列全球第一，國際客運量亦位列全球第三。而1997年通車的<span style=\"color: red;\">青馬大橋</span>曾獲美國建築界權威人士選為「20世紀十大建築」，亦是連接<span style=\"color: red;\">香港國際機場</span>與香港市區的主要幹線"},{"pid":"fa5ba5dc05573bacd94f6efb65834c511775fb19","tid":851730,"uid":15826,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a0bd06db8d97be5d2290e49a0261bc77477fc128","tid":851730,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:20:03.000Z","msg":"他亦指赤鱲角香港國際機場啟用20年來，大大推動香港空運發展，航空貨運量連續8年位列全球第一，國際客運量亦位列全球第三。而1997年通車的<span style=\"color: red;\">青馬大橋</span>曾獲美國建築界權威人士選為「20世紀十大建築」，亦是連接<span style=\"color: red;\">香港國際機場</span>與香港市區的主要幹線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"關港共撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n企開啲啦 屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d96445f76550b83344a38218399d8831d38d10a","tid":851730,"uid":201732,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"大英帝國恩賜之物"},{"pid":"ace9758fdd8ce9d3d2c1b651b42a7ce3810c50a7","tid":851730,"uid":9956,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:23:35.000Z","msg":"以前嘅玫瑰園咁成功都係靠英國咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5c499758923e4e4a8dd142653c20008672fab6","tid":851730,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:24:25.000Z","msg":"屌 燒晒香港d錢"},{"pid":"e818806bdf4f053f9fb7af9ee251f4cf16997a95","tid":851730,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:25:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cb748ed0f6edcf87e0533828bbc247c6ddb89b8","tid":851730,"uid":46192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:25:12.000Z","msg":"輸入外勞啦屌"},{"pid":"82dc451ddd22c94c88c1b5b8a0c818befe0f0387","tid":851730,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d人話咩基建會玩完, 咪傻啦<br />\n班工程佬失哂業果日你地咩唔咩得起先"},{"pid":"3e71f0321f1edd37f6452fcd724bea60885a7c28","tid":851730,"uid":54777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:26:06.000Z","msg":"佢又冇講錯喎<br />\n2047年後都係未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錢都回祖國了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae0a5228100ad6918f02c4eda10aef916b1233c","tid":851730,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:26:30.000Z","msg":"永續civil <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔撚驚爆煲了"},{"pid":"8dd73807cefb296b7acb07ebb00869ef2e4dfcdf","tid":851730,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:28:42.000Z","msg":"仲可以有咩基建？"},{"pid":"d79cc9f0cdc3258026b25e8b5e79011dbabd48c6","tid":851730,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dd73807cefb296b7acb07ebb00869ef2e4dfcdf","tid":851730,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:28:42.000Z","msg":"仲可以有咩基建？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:57:12.000Z","msg":"1）擴建鐵路、高速公路解決返工返學塞車逼鐵問題<br />\n2）開山填海，解決人均居住面積問題<br />\n3）起醫院、大形護老院，解決安老、醫療問題<br />\n4）新化淡廠/新電廠投資，解決長遠供水、供電<br />\n5）舊區重建/維修，解決70年以上嘅樓齡安全問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得以上咁多項，10年應該洗唔到1萬億咁多，太大貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 3000億10年就差唔多<br />\n1000億，各區鐵路、公路、道路擴建<br />\n1000億，新填海區（10年為1期，起碼分2期填）<br />\n400億，各區綜地改建護老院、醫院（60億一間醫院/護老院）<br />\n化淡廠<br />\n200億，化淡廠、電廠（包埋搬咩污水廠入岩洞）<br />\n剩低個400億，收樓，舊區重建<br />\n<br />\n1萬億真係on99,都唔撚夠咁多工人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大陸d料又搶貴埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec10f683f34b4b0737fe61639e177ac3c2d0e15","tid":851730,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T13:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}